on, 22 Jan 2024 10:53:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/foreign-auto-brands-boost-exports-china-sales-remain-weak-data-2024-01-22/</guid></item><item><title>汇丰银行董事长对中国投资“充满信心”，会见副行长 - 官方媒体</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-chair-confident-china-investment-meets-vice-president-state-media-2024-01-22/</link><description>据官方新华社报道，中国国家副主席韩正周一在北京会见汇丰银行董事长马克·塔克，敦促这家银行业巨头深化与中国的合作，以提高香港的金融中心地位。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 10:49:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-chair-confident-china-investment-meets-vice-president-state-media-2024-01-22/</guid></item><item><title>2023年中国住宅丧失抵押品赎回权将增加43%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-residential-foreclosures-increase-43-2023-2024-01-22/</link><description>周一的一项私人调查显示，2023年中国止赎房屋数量同比增长43%，突显出在房地产市场持续低迷和经济复苏不平衡的情况下，抵押贷款拖欠率上升的令人担忧的趋势。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 10:17:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-residential-foreclosures-increase-43-2023-2024-01-22/</guid></item><item><title>尽管经济放缓，北京仍提高了2024年的增长目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/beijing-sets-2024-growth-target-higher-despite-slowing-economy-2024-01-22/</link><description>尽管国民经济增长预期放缓，但中国首都北京仍设定了2024年5%左右的增长目标，超过了去年4.5%以上的目标。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 09:57:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/beijing-sets-2024-growth-target-higher-despite-slowing-economy-2024-01-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国在漫画中警告其稀土面临“海外”威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-comic-strip-warns-overseas-threats-its-rare-earths-2024-01-22/</link><description>中国首席情报机构在社交媒体上发布了一幅连环漫画，其中有外国角色秘密开采稀土，故事描绘了中国的战略金属受到贪婪的“海外组织”的威胁。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 09:30:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-comic-strip-warns-overseas-threats-its-rare-earths-2024-01-22/</guid></item><item><title>德国12月对美国和中国的出口大幅下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/german-exports-us-china-fall-sharply-december-2024-01-22/</link><description>根据统计局周一的数据，去年年底，德国对美国和中国等最重要的海外贸易伙伴的出口大幅下降。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 09:29:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/german-exports-us-china-fall-sharply-december-2024-01-22/</guid></item><item><title>碧桂园的离岸债券持有人选择柯克兰进行债务重组谈判 - 消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/country-gardens-offshore-bondholders-pick-kirkland-debt-revamp-talks-source-2024-01-22/</link><description>一位知情人士称，碧桂园的一大海外债权人已任命凯易律师事务所为法律顾问，此举旨在与这家违约的中国开发商讨论债务偿还方案。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 09:12:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/country-gardens-offshore-bondholders-pick-kirkland-debt-revamp-talks-source-2024-01-22/</guid></item><item><title>分析师表示，受损的俄罗斯燃料综合体的运营预计将在几周内恢复</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/analysts-see-russian-fuel-complex-resuming-operations-within-weeks-after-2024-01-22/</link><description>分析师周一表示，俄罗斯能源公司诺瓦泰克可能会在几周内恢复其乌斯季卢加加工综合体和波罗的海码头的大规模运营，此前，疑似无人机袭击导致石脑油流向亚洲中断。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 09:06:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/analysts-see-russian-fuel-complex-resuming-operations-within-weeks-after-2024-01-22/</guid></item><item><title>台湾12月出口订单创六个月来最严重跌幅，前景不佳</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwan-dec-export-orders-worst-fall-6-months-outlook-poor-2024-01-22/</link><description>台湾12月份出口订单降幅超出预期，创六个月来最差表现，由于对全球经济增长的疑虑日益加剧，台湾高科技产品的前景仍然不佳。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 08:59:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwan-dec-export-orders-worst-fall-6-months-outlook-poor-2024-01-22/</guid></item><item><title>独家：随着股市暴跌，中国采取行动支持人民币</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/china-moves-support-yuan-stock-markets-tumble-sources-2024-01-22/</link><description>四位知情人士称，中国主要国有银行周一采取行动支持人民币，收紧离岸外汇市场的流动性，同时随着股市下跌，在岸积极抛售美元。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 08:44:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/china-moves-support-yuan-stock-markets-tumble-sources-2024-01-22/</guid></item><item><title>在对限制查阅裁决的计划提出强烈抗议后，中国誓言司法披露</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-vows-judicial-disclosure-after-outcry-over-plan-curb-access-rulings-2024-01-22/</link><description>在限制查阅法院判决的计划遭到律师和法律专家不同寻常的公开批评后，中国最高法院承诺“深化司法公开”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 08:10:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-vows-judicial-disclosure-after-outcry-over-plan-curb-access-rulings-2024-01-22/</guid></item><item><title>诺瓦泰克的乌斯季卢加波罗的海燃料综合设施受到攻击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/novateks-ust-luga-baltic-sea-fuel-complex-under-attack-2024-01-22/</link><description>俄罗斯能源公司诺瓦泰克 (Novatek) 周日被迫暂停乌斯季卢加 (Ust-Luga) 的部分业务，乌斯季卢加是波罗的海的一个大型燃料出口码头和加工综合体，原因是乌克兰媒体称是无人机袭击引发的火灾。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 07:24:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/novateks-ust-luga-baltic-sea-fuel-complex-under-attack-2024-01-22/</guid></item></channel></rss>